# Project Closure Note

This lab was archived after reaching a stable proof-of-concept stage.

## Final State
- DigitalOcean private VPC lab with bastion, two web nodes, and one AI node
- Bastion used as control plane and Ansible management host
- Private FastAPI SOC assistant deployed on the AI node
- SOC CLI on bastion supported health checks and alert triage workflows

## Reason for Closure
The project met its initial learning goals, and I decided to shift focus to other projects.

## What I Would Improve Next Time
- Standardized triage response schema
- More realistic telemetry ingestion
- Dedicated `/explain`, `/hunt`, and `/note` API endpoints
- Optional private LLM/RAG architecture after deterministic triage maturity
